title: Marvel Now - 09/25/2013
description:
Hello everybody! Here we are with a new week of Marvel Now Comics!

The special mention of this week goes to:

- Avengers 20, Avengers Assemble 19, Nova 8 and Superior Spider-Man Team up 3, all Tie-Ins of "Infinity", plus the new tie-in Infinity the Heist, the first issue of a mini-series in 4 parts.

- The return of Frank Castle in "Punisher: Trials of the Punisher"

- The new chapter of "Battle of Atom", in Wolverine and X-Men 36

So, for this week is all, see ya sson, people, and enjoy the Marvel Universe!
